---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "IV Infusions | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "Hydration and nutrient support tailored to your goals.", "canonical": "/services/vitamin-injections/iv-infusions", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate bg-neutral-950 text-white">
  <!-- HERO full-bleed -->
  <div class="relative pt-28 md:pt-32">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-neutral-900 via-neutral-900/90 to-neutral-950"></div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pb-10">
      <nav class="text-sm text-white/60 mb-4">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-white/90">Home</a>
        <span class="mx-1">/</span>
        <a href="/services" class="hover:text-white/90">Services</a>
        <span class="mx-1">/</span>
        <span class="text-white/90">IV Infusions</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">IV Infusions</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/80 text-lg max-w-3xl">Hydration and nutrient support tailored to your goals.</p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-white/80">Consultation‑first</span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-white/80">Personalized plan</span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-white/80">Clear aftercare</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- QUICK CHIPS -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pb-4">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-sm">
      <a href="#glance" class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-white/80 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5">At a Glance</a>
      <a href="#indications" class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-white/80 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5">Indications</a>
      <a href="#candidates" class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-white/80 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5">Who it's for</a>
      <a href="#steps" class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-white/80 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5">Procedure Steps</a>
      <a href="#results" class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-white/80 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5">Results & Longevity</a>
      <a href="#aftercare" class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-white/80 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5">Aftercare</a>
      <a href="#faqs" class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-white/80 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5">FAQs</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pb-24 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
    <!-- Wide content -->
    <article class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-10">
      <section id="glance" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">At a Glance</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-800 p-4">
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Session length</p>
            <p class="text-white font-medium mt-1">~30–60 minutes</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-800 p-4">
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Downtime</p>
            <p class="text-white font-medium mt-1">Minimal for most</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-800 p-4">
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Discomfort</p>
            <p class="text-white font-medium mt-1">Mild to moderate (managed)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-800 p-4">
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Maintenance</p>
            <p class="text-white font-medium mt-1">Personalized plan</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="indications" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Indications</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-white/80">Your provider will map specific concerns and match techniques/products to suit your anatomy and goals.</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-white/80 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Common concerns addressed vary by service and area.</li>
          <li>Plans respect balance, symmetry, and proportionality.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="candidates" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Who It’s For (and Not For)</h3>
        <div class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-800 p-4">
            <p class="text-white/90 font-medium">Good Fit</p>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-white/80 list-disc pl-5">
              <li>Healthy individuals with realistic expectations</li>
              <li>Specific concerns that align with the service</li>
              <li>Commitment to aftercare and maintenance</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-800 p-4">
            <p class="text-white/90 font-medium">May Not Be Ideal</p>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-white/80 list-disc pl-5">
              <li>Certain medical conditions or medications</li>
              <li>Active infections or skin irritation in treatment area</li>
              <li>Unrealistic timelines or expectations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-white/70 text-sm">Educational only—not medical advice. Review your history with your provider.</p>
      </section>

      <section id="steps" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Procedure Steps</h3>
        <ol class="mt-3 list-decimal pl-5 space-y-2 text-white/80">
          <li>Consultation & goal setting</li>
          <li>Customized technique/product or device selection</li>
          <li>Treatment and immediate post‑care</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section id="results" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Results & Longevity</h3>
        <div class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-white/80">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-800 p-4"><p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Onset</p><p class="text-white font-medium mt-1">Varies by service</p></div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-800 p-4"><p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Peak</p><p class="text-white font-medium mt-1">Discussed at consult</p></div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-800 p-4"><p class="text-white/70 text-sm">Duration</p><p class="text-white font-medium mt-1">Maintenance as advised</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="aftercare" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Aftercare Checklist</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-white/80 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Follow your personalized post‑care handout.</li>
          <li>Protect the area and avoid irritants as directed.</li>
          <li>Hydrate, rest, and use recommended products only.</li>
          <li>Report unexpected reactions promptly.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="faqs" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">FAQs</h3>
        <div class="mt-3 space-y-4 text-white/80">
          <details class="group rounded-lg border border-white/10 p-4">
            <summary class="font-medium text-white cursor-pointer">How many sessions will I need?</summary>
            <p class="mt-2">It varies by concern and modality. Your provider will outline a personalized plan and maintenance if appropriate.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="group rounded-lg border border-white/10 p-4">
            <summary class="font-medium text-white cursor-pointer">Will it look natural?</summary>
            <p class="mt-2">Our approach focuses on subtle, harmonious changes that complement your features.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="group rounded-lg border border-white/10 p-4">
            <summary class="font-medium text-white cursor-pointer">Is there downtime?</summary>
            <p class="mt-2">Most services have minimal downtime. Temporary redness, swelling, or sensitivity can occur and usually resolves quickly.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </section>

      <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">*Informational content only; not medical advice. Individual results vary.</p>
    </article>

    <!-- Right column for optional highlights -->
    <aside class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-6">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold">Highlights</h4>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-white/80 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Tailored protocols and premium products/devices</li>
          <li>Comfort‑forward techniques</li>
          <li>Clear guidance and realistic timelines</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold">Good to Know</h4>
        <p class="mt-2 text-white/80">We’ll review your goals, medical history, and preferences to create a plan that suits your lifestyle and budget.</p>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
